Architecture: armel
Provides: fso-gsmd-platform
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, fso-gsmd (= ${binary:Version}), fso-deviced-ezx
Description: freesmartphone.org GSM daemon for motorola ezx devices
